brief_title: Women's Estrogen/Progestin Lipid Lowering Hormone Atherosclerosis Regression Trial (WELL-HART)
brief_summary: To determine the effects, in postmenopausal women, of hormone replacement therapy on progression/regression of coronary heart disease, as measured by quantitative angiography.
condition: Cardiovascular Diseases Coronary Disease Heart Diseases Myocardial Ischemia Postmenopause
eligibility_criteria: Postmenopausal women with angiographically-documented coronary disease. Approximately 70 percent minority
